<subSubSection id="94257B01BFA5CE8B4208AF1EB42E4A2A" pageId="4" pageNumber="71" type="type material">
<paragraph id="72DBAB99C37BE9945A5D6FBA3F930CC3" pageId="4" pageNumber="71">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6CAEDC10721BDC2E467EB4C6904FE76A" pageId="4" pageNumber="71">Holotype, SBMNH 235142, conjoined shell and anatomy, length 2.5 mm, height 1.5 mm. Holotype comprises two conjoined valves, with anatomy, preserved in 70% ethyl alcohol. Given its wet preservation and small size we were unable to capture high quality photographs of the holotype.</paragraph>
