), specimens mounted on SEM stub; Figure 1A length 2.45 mm, height 1.45 mm; Figure 1B length 2.55 mm, height 1.45 mm; Figure 1C length 2.61 mm, height 1.63 mm.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="39335032994A0A25AAEC65C251585F08" pageId="4" pageNumber="71">3 Paratypes, SBMNH 235142, same locality as holotype (preserved in 100% EtOH).</paragraph>
